{
  "stem": "15393.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, that was-- I'll start from here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the 31st of August, 1939, my father put my mother and the two of us-- two children-- on a train going from Cracow to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was-- the war was very imminent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was hanging in the air by that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was quite a bit of panic around and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, to be quite honest, I don't think anybody expected it just there and then.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was hanging, suspended in the air.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were all aware.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody was sort of preparing for it, but that it will happen the following day-- we, anyway the civilian population hardly knew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we put us on the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He, himself, stayed behind because, as he said, oh, he has to arrange a few more things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I'll join you in a day or two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my grandparents lived there and because whoever could was trying to get away, as far as possible, from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One expected that they would occupy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if so, one wanted to be as far as possible away from them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we went east.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were in this particularly lucky position, if you will, that, that we had where to go, to whom to go to.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Many people didn't-- just went to the unknown, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went to my mother's parents, my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he put us on the train, and we went on that train every year before, as I said.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went for Pesach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was always a great adventure for us children to go on the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not like today.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in those days, it was quite a journey, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
